&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Site 03:<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp The Test<br>
<br>
<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp It was three people in a circle, each with their hands stuck to each other while crossing their legs.  That was my picture.  That was my vision.  I thought about what my mother had said and began to relies that it was all true.  I was tired, and exhausted of all the “excitement” that had happened in the day.  I went to lie down.<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp I looked at my hand, and it began to blur away.  I found myself in a forest, where I saw a man fighting some sort of a strange beast.  When I saw what he did to defend himself, I ducked.  I think that I was only able to see what he had done, maybe the beast couldn’t see.  If this was what I was able to do then… but how?  The beast wasn’t dead after he made that ball of energy; it had attacked rapidly and bit off his neck.  It looked at me and it’s eyes glared.  It came running to me, aiming straight for my neck.<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp “Ahh!”  I woke up screaming with sweat all over my face.  My nose was bleeding, and my pillow was soaked in blood and sweat.  My mother was next to me, holding me tight.  <br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp “It’s all right, calm down” She said softly.  I got up out of my bed and started to do what the man in my dream was doing.<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp “Mom, I’m going to try something…  better get out of the room just to be careful.”<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp “Ok.”  She went out of the room, and closed the door.  A few seconds after she left, I raised my arms into the air.  I bended my elbows to make my arms go back, and then forward.  I crouched down and put my arms to the floor as if picking something up.  Then I jumped up and made my arms go back and forward again… but before I could finish the movements, a huge light came out of my fingers.  The technique was so powerful, as if it had huge recoil to it, made me fly back on to my rooms’ door.<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp My eyes opened widely.  “Whoa! What the hell was that?!” My mom came into the room.<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp “It’s called a Glaring Call.”  She gave me a surprised look, with her eyes opened wide as well.  “Wow, you have more skill than your father did.  I’m impressed.” Turns out that I had made a burn on my wall.  <br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp “But how did you know what I did?”<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp “I have a few of my own tricks, u know.”  She smiled at me.  “It should be easy to tell how I knew what you did.”<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp With one eyebrow up and the other down I said “Um, maybe you saw through the wall, or something?”  I looked confused.<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp “You know what telekinesis is, right?”<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp “Yea, it’s when you can read other people’s minds right?”<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp “Yes, and that it how I knew what you had done, without actually looking at you.” She said as I began to blush a little.<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp “Ahem, ok.”<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp “Eh, don’t worry.  I only read your mind when you look suspicious of something.”<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp “Well, I guess I should shut my brain off now!” I said, as my voice grew.<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp “Alright, alright, I won’t use that technique anymore, Ok?”<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp “Ok”<br>
